Package testers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutomatedTester
    This class implements the automated testing functionality.
    BreadthFirstTester
    BreadthFirstTester is an extension of TreeInspiredTester and provides a coverage testing methodology in the form of a breadth-first search for a tree of pages and their elements.
    DepthFirstTester
    DepthFirstTester is an extension of TreeInspiredTester and provides a coverage testing methodology in the form of a depth-first search for a tree of pages and their elements.
    LogReplayTester
    Takes the file from the path indicated at the start of server, and run through the same commands stored in the log file from a PREVIOUS runthrough.
    RandomTester  
    Tester
    This class implements the master Tester functionality which multiple other testers extend.
